{"tid":2043836,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李家超局長放棄英藉盡顯愛國情懷人格高尚","createTime":"2020-05-30T16:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T17:14:06.000Z","uid":248384,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49e0c93fc4010256958d0b3b8911ba36f1faa372","tid":2043836,"uid":248384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"無論是問責官員抑或行會成員，所有人宣誓就職時都必須要放棄外國國籍，但其家人卻不在此限，尤以「前宗主國」英國的公民資格最受這群顯貴青睞，其中林鄭月娥丈夫及兩名兒子皆為英國籍，陳茂波妻子及兩名子女亦是英國人；李家超雖然已放棄英籍，但相信其妻子及兩名兒子仍然保留英國公民資格；而鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶為加拿大籍，黃錦星妻子及女兒據報亦已移民加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n想必一眾人格高尚愛國愛港既膠官一定會全家投入祖國既懷抱，以身作則鄙視外國勢力，而偉大既祖國一定會堅決支持。"},{"pid":"15b33f7cd64668219eaecbc8e8ef9ed5fea3a705","tid":2043836,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"一日內咁多便衣狗帶人走？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2043807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2043807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ER1FBFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FER1FBFe.jpg&h=e7cf0576&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ca5ce1e2a0b65d1549cd699a8379a1e34cdeaab","tid":2043836,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T17:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8a57gPD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8a57gPD.png&h=02ac687c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae732356292e38314e6da652b7e0173da9feac6b","tid":2043836,"uid":248384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"那些口說愛國但子女在別國接受教育的人肯定是挾洋自重喪心病狂，你們要記住祖國沒欠你們的。"},{"pid":"941ef93d4d7abcec9aaa36469fc4a8a12a620559","tid":2043836,"uid":221913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/UntriedEdibleCrane-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FUntriedEdibleCrane-size_restricted.gif&h=9374c2f4&s={SIZE}